OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome late brightness this evening.
OL,7,FArgyll will have the best of the sunny
OL,8,Fthen clear spells, while the Glasgow
OL,9,Farea will become generally cloudier.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FDry and bright with
OL,12,Fvariable cloud. The best chance of
OL,13,Fbrighter or sunnier spells in the
OL,14,Fafternoon, particularly across Argyll.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,17,FMainly dry and very warm on Thursday
OL,18,Fwith sunny spells. Cloudier, cooler on
OL,19,FFriday with showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,20,FRain spreading east on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
